original_title: หนังสือรุ่น
overview: From the series to cinematic version, a story of friendship and promises between two close friends. Nut and Phop are high school friends, but their friendship breaks from unknown reason. One day, they both meet once again. May be this time they will not separate.
tagline: A tear-jerking movie that make you appreciate life.
title: The YearBook Movie
